### Get Top Artists (Default: popularity desc, page 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists

### Get Artists - Page 2
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists?page=2

### Get Artists - Sort by followers ascending
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists?sortBy=followers&order=asc

### Get Artists - Custom limit
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists?limit=50

### Get Artists - Sort by followers desc, page 3, limit 10
GET http://localhost:3000/api/artists?page=3&limit=10&sortBy=followers&order=desc

