### Get Top Songs (Default: popularity desc, page 1)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/songs

### Get Songs - Page 2
GET http://localhost:3000/api/songs?page=2

### Get Songs - Sort by release date descending
GET http://localhost:3000/api/songs?sortBy=releaseDate&order=desc

### Get Songs - Sort by release date ascending (oldest first)
GET http://localhost:3000/api/songs?sortBy=releaseDate&order=asc

### Get Songs - Custom limit
GET http://localhost:3000/api/songs?limit=100

### Get Songs - Sort by popularity asc, page 5, limit 25
GET http://localhost:3000/api/songs?page=5&limit=25&sortBy=popularity&order=asc
